NSAW TMB Training Workshops May 8th

Before the workshop

Please make sure you have R, TMB, and an R IDE installed. Please see Getting Started with TMB for software requirements and package installation instructions. The TMB Developer Resources provide a collection of useful resources from the TMB developers

NSAW Agendas

Beginner TMB (9:00am - 12:30pm)

Training Materials are found under the docs directory

Download materials

You can install materials from GitHub with:

# install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("NSAWTraining/TMBtraining")
